
Given a list of numbers, find all pairs that sum to a target value.
-->brute force
l=[1,2,3,4,5]  #t=9
target=9
for i in range(len(l)) :
        for j in range(i+1,len(l)):
            if l[i]+l[j]==target:
              print((l[i],l[j]))

TC = O(n²)
SC = O(1)


optimized approach-->using hashset
l=[2, 7, 11, 15, 3, 6]  #t=9
target=9
seen=set()
for i in l:
    complement=target-i

    if complement in seen:
        print((complement,i))

    seen.add(i)
TC = O(n)
SC = O(n)
